      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/png;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" /alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eCollection Management Business User App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThis Collection Management App helps businesses optimize cash flow by predicting which customers are likely to pay on time and which may delay payments beyond 30 days. Using uploaded invoice data, the app applies machine learning models to provide insights such as late payment trends, Paydex score patterns, collection status summaries, credit check outcomes, and the relationship between revenue, \r\n    outstanding, and write-off amounts.\t\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eUpload collection data, select a trained model, match required features, and initiate prediction.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eThe app returns predicted customer payment behavior, visual charts of payment risk distribution, and transaction-level summaries to guide follow-ups and collection strategies.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eCustomer Risk Prediction: Identify likely defaulters using H2O DRF model trained on invoice data.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eUpload \u0026 Predict: Upload your own data and run predictions using pre-trained models.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eVisual Analytics: View customer distribution, transaction summaries, and payment behavior.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eCustom Feature Selection: Match your dataset with model requirements for accurate forecasting.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e",
